    <short-description type="string">
      A view for remote controling RC models and larger flying objects.
    </short-description>

    <long-description type="string">
      RCView is a flightgear addon setting-up a new view which mimics
      the vision of a pilot remote controlling a plane.

      The RC pilot looks at the plane at all times and does not
      move. However, a configuration menu allows you to set your
      height and the distance at which you start remote controlling
      the target.

      During the flight, you can jump to another location nearby the
      plane, which could be useful if you have lost your model or
      crashed it in a nearby field.
    </long-description>

